		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Calculating the day of the week</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p>This article details various mathematical <a href="/wiki/Algorithm" title="Algorithm">algorithms</a> to <b>calculate the day of the week</b> for any particular date in the past or future.</p>
<p>A typical application is to calculate the day of the week on which someone was born or some other special event occurred.</p>
